'''OVH'''，全名'''OVH Groupe SAS'''，[[法国|法国]][[雲端運算|雲端運算]]公司，提供有[[虚拟专用服务器|VPS]]、[[专有服务器|专有服务器]]及其他[[Web|Web]]服务。OVH拥有一个全球面积最大的[[数据中心|数据中心]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why OVH opened the world’s largest datacentre in the Great White North|url=https://www.itworldcanada.com/article/why-ovh-opened-the-worlds-largest-datacentre-in-the-great-white-north/387358|accessdate=2019-10-16|author=Wood|date=2016-10-12|first=Eric Emin|work=www.itworldcanada.com|publisher=International Data Group, Inc. (IDG) [[国际数据集团|IT World Canada]]|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20191016075644/https://www.itworldcanada.com/article/why-ovh-opened-the-worlds-largest-datacentre-in-the-great-white-north/387358|archivedate=2019-10-16}}</ref>它是[[欧洲|欧洲]]最大的[[互联网托管服务|互联网托管服务]]提供商<ref>{{Cite web|title=How VMware Is Transforming Itself Into a Multi-Cloud Company|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/05/26/how-vmware-is-transforming-itself-into-a-multi-cloud-company/|accessdate=2019-10-16|author=MSV|date=2019-05-26|first=Janakiram|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190619035921/https://www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/05/26/how-vmware-is-transforming-itself-into-a-multi-cloud-company/|archivedate=2019-06-19}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Canadian customers’ heads are still in the clouds, and so is VMware’s {{!}} Financial Post|url=https://www.itworldcanada.com/article/canadian-customers-heads-are-still-in-the-clouds-and-so-is-vmwares/421294|accessdate=2019-10-16|author=Coop|date=2019-08-27|first=Alex|work=[[金融郵報|Financial Post]]|language=en-CA|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20191016035105/https://business.financialpost.com/technology/tech-news/canadian-customers-heads-are-still-in-the-clouds-and-so-is-vmwares|archivedate=2019-10-16}}</ref>，也是全球第三大基于物理服务器的托管服务提供商。<ref>{{Cite web|title=World's third-largest hosting provider OVH opens Melbourne office|url=http://www.crn.com.au/news/worlds-third-largest-hosting-provider-ovh-opens-melbourne-office-461480|accessdate=2019-10-16|author=Sarraf|date=2017-05-12|first=Samira|work=CRN Australia|publisher={{tsl|en|nextmedia}}|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20191016030105/https://www.crn.com.au/news/worlds-third-largest-hosting-provider-ovh-opens-melbourne-office-461480|archivedate=2019-10-16}}</ref>该公司由Klaba家族于1999年成立<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=French firm to open 1st US data center in Fauquier Co.|url=https://wtop.com/business-finance/2016/10/french-firm-to-open-1st-us-data-center-in-fauquier-co/|accessdate=2019-10-16|author=Clabaugh|date=2016-10-06|first=Jeff|work={{tsl|en|WTOP-FM||WTOP}}|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20191016043217/https://wtop.com/business-finance/2016/10/french-firm-to-open-1st-us-data-center-in-fauquier-co/|archivedate=2019-10-16}}</ref>，总部位于[[法国|法国]][[鲁贝|鲁贝]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-ovh-strategy-idUKKCN1MS17L|title=France's OVH to triple spending to take on Google, Amazon in cloud computing|author=Rosemain|first=Mathieu|date=2018-10-18|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2019-11-07|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20191107020421/https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-ovh-strategy/frances-ovh-to-triple-spending-to-take-on-google-amazon-in-cloud-computing-idUKKCN1MS17L|archivedate=2019-11-07|author2=Barzic|first2=Gwénaëlle|language=en}}</ref>OVH是按{{tsl|en|Law of France|法國法律}}成立的{{tsl|en|société par actions simplifiée||简化股份制公司}}。

== 历史与成长 ==
Octave Klaba于1999年11月<ref name=":0" />在三个家庭成员（Henry，Haline和Miroslaw）的帮助下成立。

2016年10月，OVH据报筹集了2.5亿美元以进一步扩大国际业务。<ref>{{Cite web|title=OVH Partners with KKR and TowerBrook for Further Global Expansion|url=http://exithub.com/klaba-family-ovh-europe-no-1-web-host-raises-e250m-from-kkr-towerbrook/|accessdate=9 January 2017|work=exithub|archive-date=2019-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016075653/https://exithub.com/klaba-family-ovh-europe-no-1-web-host-raises-e250m-from-kkr-towerbrook/}}</ref>该轮融资使OVH的估值超10亿美元。据报道，OVH在2016财年的收入为3.2亿欧元。 OVH于2018年宣布自2021年开始将投资增加三倍的五年计划。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ovh-strategy-idUSKCN1MS17L|title=France's OVH to triple spending to take on Google, Amazon in cloud...|author=Rosemain|first=Mathieu|date=2018-10-18|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2019-09-07|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190907000557/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ovh-strategy/frances-ovh-to-triple-spending-to-take-on-google-amazon-in-cloud-computing-idUSKCN1MS17L|archivedate=2019-09-07|author2=Barzic|first2=Gwénaëlle|language=en}}</ref>

2017年6月，OVH 通过债务融资再次募集了4亿欧元资金，本轮由 [[JP_Morgan_Chase|JP Morgan Chase]] 领投，CIC Nord Ouest和Banque Commerciale du Marché Nord Europe跟投。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mg21.com/ovhcloud.html|title=欧洲最大全球第三主机及服务器提供商：OVH Groupe SAS (OVHcloud)|publisher=mg21.com|date=2021-08-16|access-date=2021-08-17|archive-date=2021-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817154651/https://www.mg21.com/ovhcloud.html}}</ref>

截至2018年，OVH已在19个国家/地区拥有27个数据中心，托管30万台服务器。<ref>{{Cite web|title=About - OVH Canada|url=https://www.ovh.com/ca/en/about-us/|accessdate=2018-07-09|publisher=OVH|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709204140/https://www.ovh.com/ca/en/about-us/|archivedate=2018-07-09}}</ref>该公司在许多[[欧洲|欧洲]]国家以及[[北美洲|北美洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]和[[新加坡|新加坡]]提供[[本地化|本地化]]服务，如客户服务办公室。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Best dedicated server hosting providers of 2019|url=https://www.techradar.com/news/best-dedicated-server-hosting-providers|accessdate=2019-09-06|author=Williams|date=2019-08-26|first=Mike|work={{tsl|en|TechRadar}}|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190906235716/https://www.techradar.com/news/best-dedicated-server-hosting-providers|archivedate=2019-09-06}}</ref>{{As of|2019}}，OVH是世界上最大的云计算提供商之一，拥有超过一百万客户，且是世界上最大的[[OpenStack|OpenStack]]部署之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=OVH pulls gloves off bare metal fighters as it eyes up US cloud vendors|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/04/29/ovh_adds_bare_metal_fighters_to_its_roster_looking_to_challenge_the_us_cloud_dominance/|accessdate=2020-04-18|author=Max Smolaks|date=2019-04-29|work=www.theregister.co.uk|archive-date=2020-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403124053/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/04/29/ovh_adds_bare_metal_fighters_to_its_roster_looking_to_challenge_the_us_cloud_dominance/}}</ref>

OVH也以其提供的{{tsl|en|email hosting service|电子邮箱托管服务}}闻名<ref>{{Cite web|title=OVH lance une offre E-mail Pro basée sur Microsoft Exchange... mais sans ActiveSync|url=https://www.nextinpact.com/news/103418-ovh-lance-offre-e-mail-pro-basee-sur-microsoft-exchange-mais-sans-activesync.htm|accessdate=2020-04-18|author=David Legrand|date=2017-03-27|work=www.nextinpact.com|language=fr|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327103511/https://www.nextinpact.com/news/103418-ovh-lance-offre-e-mail-pro-basee-sur-microsoft-exchange-mais-sans-activesync.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Press release for market report|url=https://www.arnnet.com.au/mediareleases/77901/us-email-hosting-services-market-is-slated-to/|date=2020|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321133500/https://www.arnnet.com.au/mediareleases/77901/us-email-hosting-services-market-is-slated-to/}}</ref>。

