== 环境影响 ==
OVH于2003年开始在其数据中心整合创新型液冷。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Servers on Demand: Custom Water-Cooled Servers in One Hour|url=https://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2013/09/16/ovh-servers|date=September 16, 2013|work=Data Center Knowledge|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321133718/https://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2013/09/16/ovh-servers}}</ref>

OVH在很大程度上依赖[[核电|核电]]，尤其是其Gravelines数据中心以紧靠{{tsl|en|Gravelines Nuclear Power Station||Gravelines核电站}}闻名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Energy efficient datacenter|url=https://www.fenercom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2017-05-04-Water-cooling-with-free-cooling-to-have-a-very-low-power-usage-effectiveness-OVH-fenercom.pdf|author=Julien Costagliola di Fiore|date=2017-05-04|publisher=OVH|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316031443/https://www.fenercom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2017-05-04-Water-cooling-with-free-cooling-to-have-a-very-low-power-usage-effectiveness-OVH-fenercom.pdf}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Le nucléaire et le territoire : regards sur l’intégration spatiale des centrales en France|url=http://geoconfluences.ens-lyon.fr/informations-scientifiques/dossiers-regionaux/la-france-des-territoires-en-mutation/articles-scientifiques/nucleaire-territoires-france|author=Teva Meyer|date=2017-12-11|publisher=[[ENS_Lyon|ENS Lyon]]|language=fr|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501215513/http://geoconfluences.ens-lyon.fr/informations-scientifiques/dossiers-regionaux/la-france-des-territoires-en-mutation/articles-scientifiques/nucleaire-territoires-france}}</ref>

2021年1月，OVH与其他行业参与者加入了{{tsl|en|Climate Neutral Data Centre Pact|气候中和数据中心条约}}，该条约承诺在2030年之前实现数据中心的气候中和。

